➜河南诗人田书芹：七律押平韵（三十三首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/432506073_100115135	53647
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201117/3908e912bf54427c945dfb03c814ff1c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七律押平韵（三十三首）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>白露</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仲秋时节云高爽，白露为霜早晚凉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">雁去随风无半影，花开和月有孤芳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三山锦绣桠枫茂，五岳斑斓玉桂香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杜甫诗中寻翠碧，张炎律里览幽篁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.9.8</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>随感</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凉风一缕天渐冷，落叶飘零返故乡。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苦乐年华安逸度，穷通世路太平行。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">村中处事传三载，碗里时蔬拌五粮。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">皓月星空羊左伴，桃园定住置身祥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.9.2</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>醉意重阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">重阳携友上高台，万岭金霞眉眼抬。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
