<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">得意鸳鸯依柳渡，多情溪水助波徊。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">陶公何处登临醉，游客而今笑语开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">试看群芳入佳境，迷魂荡荡到蓬莱。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.10.12</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 随感</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凉风一缕天渐冷，落叶飘零返故乡。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苦乐年华安逸度，穷通世路太平行。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">村中处事传三载，碗里时蔬拌五粮。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">皓月星空羊左伴，桃园定住置身祥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 2019.9.2</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201117/1f852435c26e48aca9723cc2eee89313.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>无题</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">岁月匆匆流逝水，相扶一世历艰辛。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风中共济为家业，雨里同舟养子亲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">早出披星赢果穗，晚归秉烛享天伦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">勤能补拙先人训，劳动光荣理最真。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.9.7</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>庆祝建国七十周年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">七十春秋天地覆，神州崛起世人惊。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">航母巡弋兵威赫，火箭翱翔太空行。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">强化推新创伟绩，铲除腐朽树廉明。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">金融发展前途发，国运恒昌快速赢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>雪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一夜西风催絮下，平铺大地着新裳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">麦苗浸润心中醉，楠竹分明梦里藏。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">素裹银装添雅韵，婷娉婀娜抒华章。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">悠悠洒洒尘埃定，化作甘霖入土香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 2019.12.2</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>月桂</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">月桂盛开无异样，馨香四溢醉秋光。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">金银意韵倾城秀，雨露精华待友尝。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">艳惹群芳花下羡，素招众客树前望。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">靓姿一展呈诗卷，风采宜人受颂扬。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.10.19</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201117/dd3a2ea6e80a483bbfb1bfd0fcf21ebe.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>重阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今又重阳催岁老，浑然不觉鬓成霜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">登高把酒思兄弟，望远临风忆爹娘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">难见双亲乘鹤去，易寻众友养家忙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">学陶采菊东篱下，醉卧吟诗话寂凉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.10.17</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>教师节感怀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一支粉笔写春秋，奉献芳华无所求。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">愿育英苗勤播种，甘抛汗水䅁低头。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孜孜备课兴科目，汲汲陪娃做子牛。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">辛苦换来丰硕果，喜看桃李竞风流。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 2019.09.10</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>中秋月夜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">悠悠岁月任蹉跎，苦闷无聊怎奈何。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">茅舍檐低宾客少，竹篱院小菊花多。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">堪怜鬓白伤心痛，顿觉花黄举足挪。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日到中秋冰镜暗，神情失落咏哀歌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.9.20</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>题图诗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">暮霞万丈水连天，隐隐奇峰藏洞仙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">早出归船忙摆渡，长行去雁急翩跹。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蛮腰碧柳翩翩舞，玉面红蕖再再传。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此境闲观真造化，浑然不觉入平川。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.10.29</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201117/2abbb8a15c5d463fb00b6cc1e446d394.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>重阳节抒怀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">恰逢佳节雨徘徊，无处登临上菊台。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只记陶潜当日醉，不闻彭泽几时回。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人间草木添新意，骚客毫端秀往来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自古至今皆若此，抒情泼墨畅胸开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.10.8</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>望海情思</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">烟波浩渺泻疏狂，舰笛先声万里航。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风急云飞峰顶俏，山青日落岸边凉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">腾腾激浪银河荡，处处推潮意气扬。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">思绪联翩涛与共，情倾碧海信天长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.2.14</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>艾草</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">路边野陌度从容，不与群芳比艳彤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风吻清香迷远近，雨临素朴涤葱茏。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无心追誉赢尊宠，有意帮人避恶凶。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">即使身微黏故土，天生灵验药王封。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.6.26</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>重阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">举杯邀月共疏狂，四处金英是菊香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丹桂无尘花雅淡，紫箫有韵调高慷。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今时北斗长天耀，昔日东风大地扬。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">九九忘归不忍去，题诗咏赞在山岗。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.10.22</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201117/e9d7da568960448b90d700c5b392a637.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>滨海踏沙行</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那天滨海踏沙行，雪浪滔滔击岸声。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日照粼粼千虑少，云浮淡淡一身轻。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">潮来潮去潮如涌，毫舞毫飞毫自耕。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">暮色降临霞绘染，矶头壁上看潮平。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.10.30</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>题图诗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">月夜星繁两比肩，苍穹漠漠爽蓝天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凤鸾互敬崇仙侣，琴瑟和鸣共手拳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自古柔情甜似蜜，如今荡耳暖于绵。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诗情画意人间爱，畅意欢歌视影旋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.7.17</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>秋意</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹 </strong> </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">昨日繁星布皓苍，今朝冷气袭荷塘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">依稀帘幕疏桐影，寥落楼台淡月光。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唤至陶公采篱菊，招来张籍赋秋霜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">临风把酒何人醉？研墨挥毫抒异香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.9.23</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>访菊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹 </strong> </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">漫踏芳园独自游，风姿婀娜菊清幽。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">馨香醉了花前月，雅韵添来枝上头。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">久立无声情切切，长吟不尽兴悠悠。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">愿君能解侬之意，莫负今朝泼墨留。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.9.22</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201117/bb5cf4e90e5b4eccab96105f63d59235.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>庆祝建国七十周年 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹 </strong> </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">华夏腾飞日益新，富饶昌盛乐黎民。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">扬眉吐气蓝天上，昂首挺胸沧海巡。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丝路开通达民意，金融发展沐阳春。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">山河锦绣多辽阔，国富家安道法遵。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>秋意</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">玉露轻轻吻叶凉，星辉映水闪银光。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">溪边垂柳盈盈舞，陇上鸣琴袅袅扬。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">浊酒三杯昏浅醉，新词一阙意深长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">邀婵共赏秋之韵，浩荡昭昭显着彰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.10.13</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 腊八情</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">腊八家家煮粥锅，杂粮豆果核桃多。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">调和万物增顔色，聚合千灵敬佛陀。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">容纳醇香储百味，收存桔脯藏千禾。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">带来节日亲情重，滋养纯良美善歌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.1.1</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>元旦感言</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">窗外闲吟伴艳阳，躬身研墨赋诗章。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">玉猪驮瑞辞星岁，金鼠呈祥送福乡。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不念人生烦恼事，更教眼底畅心房。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">激情燃起胸豪迈，昂首风霜信手扬。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.1.1</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201117/5cb8df2a06e14cdda526e5152bd878f4.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>新年感赋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">换岁神州喜气天，回春大地瑞光燃。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和风送走瘟情险，细雨迎来吉庆年。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爆竹声声辞旧赋，梅花点点抒新篇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诗心愿化三江水，洒满人间梦也圆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.1.25</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>战瘟神</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">八面精英智慧多，疫情猖獗岂如何？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">专家日夜寻源本，护士朝昏探病魔。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万里条条关卡设，千村处处避瘟波。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">东君欲问灾民事，人定胜天咏凯歌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.1.29</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>赞钟南山</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">八十高龄战险关，英雄钟老号南山。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为民不惜身心倦，忧国还将疫病攀。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大众生灵皆慎重，小家妻女乃轻闲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清标敬业诚珍贵，美誉流传震九寰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.2.1</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>秋意</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">昨日寒云布皓苍，今朝冷气袭猖狂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">萧疏草木严霜信，寥落楼台淡月光。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">瘦叶凄凄飘陌野，残荷凛凛立池塘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">菊花山上秋风劲，独有金英散异香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.9.20</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201117/9bb05c87d289423f8ff7bffeb5d5b740.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>访菊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">漫踏芳园独自游，风姿婀娜菊清幽。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">馨香醉了花前月，神韵添来叶上秋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">久立无声情切切，长吟不尽兴悠悠。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为君能解侬之意，莫负今朝访客留。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.9.21</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>沉痛哀悼六爹驾鹤西游</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>——2019.12.13晚仙逝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哀悼尊严驾鹤游，寒风凛冽泣啼稠。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">惊闻昨夜身增病，变作今晨泪噎喉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一世清廉公正性，十分简淡实诚求。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">铮铮傲骨天堂驻，早有彩云仙驾侯。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.12.18</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>庆端阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云淡风轻粽子香，万民一起庆端阳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">菖蒲艾叶门前挂，糯米咸蛋室内芳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">五色彩绒身脖系，六颜香袋腹胸妆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">举杯共饮同恭贺，祖国昌盛岁永疆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.6.26（旧作修改）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>题图诗《九九时》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一路金黄一路诗，自然美景自然姿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两边排列花惊世，四面环看树整枝。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">笑脸迎人招远客，风声伴我赋新词。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而今有你增秋色，挥笔正逢九九时。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.10.25</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201117/e6d75609f2bd40d38387a0bdb7a7f84e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>咏菊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寿客婆娑倩影摇，试看秋日赛春潮。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">南山遍地黄金甲，东阁千声白玉箫。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寥阔苍穹无寂寞，蹉跎岁月尽逍遥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天生魁宝奇功用，明目怡神本草标。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.11.5</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201117/a0da65cde9dd436990c90f65a04ce435.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】</strong>田书芹，河南内乡县人，喜欢体育，特长篮球，中国诗歌网会员，有多篇文章和诗词在内乡亲民网发表。诗写祖国大好河山，词写自己梦想人生！现为《星连文学社》编委。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201117/b64c685d5f7946e788ae14a135c63a02.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
